markets.title: Will Tulsi Gabbard leave the Trump Administration this year?
markets.subtitle: :: Director of National Intelligence
markets.rules_primary: If Tulsi Gabbard leaves, or it is announced they will leave, their office before Jan 1, 2026, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The person must leave their office to resolve the market to Yes. For example, if they accept another role and leave their current role, the market resolves to Yes. If they accept another role without leaving their current role, then the market does not resolve to Yes.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
